Ask HN: How can I sell my app?
text:
I’ve built a pretty polished cross platform desktop app as a side project. It it small (has a few hundred users) and is new. Since I want to focus on other projects and schoolwork, is there anywhere I can go to sell this? Or find partners to handle growth while I focus on tech?

If it helps, the app in question is at https://parallelsocial.net. Thank you for your help & advice!
